CHANGES IN VERSION 1.2.0 (2011-04, bioconductor release 2.8)
-----------------------------------------------------------------

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    - New argument handling for the 'plot' method

    - New experimental data set for examples and vignette

    - More detailed vignette


BUGS

    - Fix minor bug in the 'show' method

    - Fix missing name of the return object of the 'gsri' function

    - Correct normation of weighting functions (not relevant for results, for the sake of completeness)